      "value": "<p><em>Ever since you were a child, you've experienced vivid dreams of cutting down hordes of shrieking, twisted demons.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>Angelkin Aasimar Heritage</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p>Whenever you succeed at a critical hit with a melee weapon against an evil outsider, you ignore an amount of the outsider's damage reduction (if any) equal to the critical multiplier of your weapon (this cannot reduce a creature's damage reduction to below 0).</p>",
